# --- Postmark Email ---
# EMAIL_PROVIDER=postmark
# EMAIL_API_KEY=your-postmark-server-token
# EMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=coach@fearvana.com
# EMAIL_FROM_NAME=Akshay from Fearvana

# ============================================================================
# Development Tips
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Use mock providers for local development (default)
# 2. Mock providers require no API keys and simulate realistic behavior
# 3. Cache is enabled by default to speed up development
# 4. Circuit breakers protect against cascading failures
# 5. See src/lib/integration/config.ts for full configuration options
#
# ============================================================================
